==English==
===Noun===
'''[[just]] [[deserts]]'''
#A [[punishment]] or [[reward]] that is considered to be what the recipient [[deserve]]d.

====Usage notes====
*'''Deserts''' here is the plural of [[desert]], meaning "that which one deserves".  It is rarely used outside this phrase.
*The spelling '''just desserts''' is commonly found, but is incorrect.

